    "sents": ["Journal Pre-proof Risk factors for disease severity, unimprovement, and mortality of COVID-19 patients in Wuhan, China Risk factors for disease severity, unimprovement, and mortality of COVID-19 patients in Wuhan, China", "In conclusion, being male, as well as having severe COVID-19 symptoms, expectoration, muscle ache, and decreased albumin were shown to be independent risk factors which influence patients' improvement during follow-up.", "Older age was associated with poor conditions and outcomes in COVID-19 patients.", "Table 1 Baseline characteristics of the 663 COVID-19 patients.", "Table 2 Clinical characteristics of the 663 COVID-19 patients.", "Table 3 Laboratory results and imaging finding of the 663 COVID-19 patients."],
